phrases: You will get sick if you fall asleep here.

Information Available for Public Disclosure Field Rations

we have to wait for lifts to come so we can move the horses.

the other Titans outside the wall might still be a threat.

destination is somewhere outside of Wall Maria.

they will want to rest somewhere where Titans are unable to reach them.
